# Rust sources & build artifacts — never ship these (they bloat the VSIX
# and trip the secret scanner on StormLib's embedded verification key).
# Note: bin/ (compiled wc3 / wc3-confuse / cli.js) IS shipped and must stay.
target/**
crates/**
**/Cargo.toml
**/Cargo.lock
**/build.rs
testdata/**
docs/**
scripts/**
typings/**

